# ==============================================================
# LowKeyBD Environment Configuration Template
# ==============================================================
#
# LowKeyBD is a monorepo containing:
# 1. NestJS Backend API (located in /apps/api)
# 2. Next.js Frontend App (located in /apps/web)
#
# Please configure the environment variables in their respective folders:
# - API Configurations: Copy /apps/api/.env.example to /apps/api/.env and edit variables.
# - Web Configurations: Copy /apps/web/.env.example to /apps/web/.env and edit variables.
#
# Ensure all Docker dependencies are running via `docker-compose up -d`.
# Ports are restricted to loopback (127.0.0.1) for local development security.
